        Sources</a></font></p>
      <p> <font face="Arial, Verdana, sans-serif" size="2"><a href="iguana/igdiet.html">Iguana 
        Diet</a></font></p>
      <p> <font face="Arial, Verdana, sans-serif" size="2"><a href="prekill.html">Feeding 
        Killed Prey</a></font></p>
      <p> <font face="Arial, Verdana, sans-serif" size="2"><a href="clawtrim.html">Claw 
        Trimming</a></font></p>
      <p><font face="Arial, Verdana, sans-serif" size="2"><a href="http://www.reptile-database.org/">TIGR 
        Reptile Database</a>: Agamidae</font></p>
